column5: Hi Everybody !  I'm going on fishing trip june 28th to july 5th 2009, at caesars lodge. Our cabin will be on lake Larouche. I would like to have some feedback of anybody who has been there. Is the fishing any good ? How is the cabin ? What lures where the best for you ? Any feedback will be appreciated, thank-you.
http://www.ofncommunity.com/forums/index.php?showtopic=16506  The Lodge has been talked about take a look in the link.
thank you, but i would like feedback on lake larouche
